			<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
				<tr>
					<td vAlign="top" class="Content">Welcome to the Boone County Fire District's Emergency Preparedness web site.  It contains information and resources regarding disaster mitigation, preparedness, response and recovery for citizens, schools and businesses.  We urge all of Boone County's citizens, schools and businesses to prepare responsibly for disaster by finding out about hazards present in the community, preparing a disaster supplies kit and practicing and maintaining your disaster plan.</td>
