					<td vAlign="top" class="Content">Our &quot;goal&quot; is to help our citizens, schools and businesses prepare for and cope with any type of emergency.  A large portion of our responsibility is to educate the general public, schools and businesses on disaster preparedness and response. You will find documents related to emergency preparedness in the <a href="/emrgprep/Library/">document library</a>.  These documents can be viewed and printed with Adobe Acrobat Reader. Some files may take several minutes to download on a dial-up connection.  We hope that you find the information informative and useful.</td>
